ggpairs(iris[,1:4],aes(col=iris$Species))

Tab2: Density Plot

ggplot(iris,aes(x = iris$Sepal.Length,col = Species))+
      geom_density()+
      xlim(min(iris$Sepal.Length)*0.8,max(iris$Sepal.Length)*1.2)

tab3: Association Plot

ggplot(iris,aes(x=iris$Sepal.Length,y=iris$Petal.Width,col = Species)) +
geom_point()
